<br>
Most of the time it collects dust but in certain situations it can help a lot. <br>
<br>
Maore<br>
55th druidess of Tunare<br>
Bristlebane <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukaraethonii.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Karaethon II</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(7/24/01 8:43:18 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Glamour of Tunare's usefulness?</span><hr size=1> Someone correct me on this....but it doesn't stack with tash? I was messing around with it in chardok on dogs, but then my chanter beat me to tashing one and it wouldn't hold. stacking an extra -20mr with tash would be nice...but instead of?<br>
